name: SEO Rank Analyser
author: SEORankAnalyser.com

sections.description:
SEO Rank Analyser (Analyzer) is one stop powerful solution for On-page SEO test. This plugin check and suggest you for every elements of your website with description. You can analyze your home page and inner pages in one click.

You can contact us at support @ seorankanalyser.com for support.

Features

  • Analysis and suggestion for on-page SEO rank tester :
  • Title Tag
  • Meta Keyword and Description
  • Content Heading (from H1 to H6)
  • Images
  • Languages
  • Encoding
  • DocType
  • File Size
  • Robot.txt file
  • Favicon
  • Site Map Checking
  • Google Analytics checker
  • Page Loading Time (Speed)
  • Mobile Compatibility
  • Permanent Redirect
  • Suggest you the proper keywords for your website
  • Website grade and score
  • Content Ratio Analysis
  • Broken Link Check and Analysis
  • Easy, fast and light weight rank checker plugin

    • How it works

    This plugin just send your domain (URL) to http://seorankanalyser.com/ web site and get details data from server. All data processed in http://seorankanalyser.com and return results to your plugin’s panel.
sections.installation:
1. Download, unzip and upload to your WordPress plugins directory
  2. Click on SEO Rank Analyser from menu and get report from there
  3. Email us at
